title.narrative: Programme Operations and Technical Assistance to the Government of Nepal on Post Earthquake Reconstruction Planning

description.narrative: This activity (Programme Operations and Technical Assistance to the Government of Nepal on Post Earthquake Reconstruction Planning) is a component of Post-Earthquake Reconstruction in Nepal - Building Back Better reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Procurement of Services' and a budget of £2,756,952. This component benefits Nepal, and works in the following sector(s): Immediate post-emergency reconstruction and rehabilitation. , with the following implementing partners: Coffey International Development, Crown Agents Limited, DAI Europe, Foreign, Commonwealth and Development Office, Palladium International Ltd (UK), PwC. The start date is 15-07-2016 and the end date is 30-06-2021.
